18:27.858 --> 18:29.526
No. Yes. I mean, it won't matter.

18:29.610 --> 18:32.738
-Then eat the fucking cream puff.
-No.

18:32.821 --> 18:34.281
-Yes.
-No.

18:37.451 --> 18:40.662
I'm so sorry, Sheila.
I am so sorry. I am so sorry.

18:40.746 --> 18:42.789
You have to forgive me.
I don't know why I did that.

18:42.873 --> 18:44.291
I'm a horrible person.

18:45.083 --> 18:46.919
-It's okay. It's okay.
-What if it's not okay?

18:47.002 --> 18:48.795
-What if it's never okay, Sheila?
-It's okay.

18:48.879 --> 18:50.589
It's okay. It's okay.

18:52.257 --> 18:53.842
-Let me say her name.
-No.

18:53.926 --> 18:56.220
Back the fuck off
or I'll dropkick you in the nuts!

18:56.303 --> 18:58.222
Hey, Sheila, we got an issue here!

18:58.305 --> 19:00.349
-Don't you touch me, you monster.
-Yeah.

19:00.432 --> 19:02.851
She's my friend. It's okay.
She's my friend. Just go away.

19:02.935 --> 19:04.394
For the record, I did not touch her.

19:04.478 --> 19:05.479
-Okay.
-She touched me.

19:05.562 --> 19:06.897
-Can we talk outside?
-We need to--

19:06.980 --> 19:08.315
-We need to talk right now…
-Yes.

19:08.398 --> 19:10.067
-Outside.
-…because right now you wanna see…

19:10.150 --> 19:13.612
-This is not a good time.
-That fucking asshole is toying with the--

19:16.532 --> 19:17.533
Oh, my God.

19:18.033 --> 19:19.493
What happened to Tyler?

19:20.494 --> 19:23.080
I had a weird night. Somebody punched me.

19:23.163 --> 19:25.999
He had surgery. We need to know
what your plans are for the future

19:26.083 --> 19:28.585
because we have some serious
financial realities we're facing.

19:28.669 --> 19:30.045
And if you're just gonna bail on us

19:30.128 --> 19:31.630
like everybody else, then we're gonna--

19:31.713 --> 19:34.049
I need to lie down. Maybe a sandwich.

19:34.925 --> 19:36.426
It's election night.

19:36.510 --> 19:38.470
And the results are coming in any minute.

19:38.554 --> 19:40.055
I have a house full of guests.

19:40.138 --> 19:41.348
We don't have a house.

19:41.431 --> 19:43.141
We almost had an apartment.

19:43.225 --> 19:45.978
Now we just have a really expensive hole
in Tyler's head.

19:46.061 --> 19:49.022
