it seems like you're gonna take off

19:49.106 --> 19:51.817
on some rocket ship to money town
and leave our asses behind.

19:51.900 --> 19:53.193
That is not who I am.

19:53.277 --> 19:55.404
Liar. She has you pegged.

19:57.281 --> 20:01.910
I know that the world can seem like
a cruel and selfish place sometimes,

20:01.994 --> 20:04.788
but not everybody is like that.

20:04.872 --> 20:07.457
Some people have different values,
like kindness.

20:07.541 --> 20:11.295
You lying sack of shit.
She sees who you are.

20:11.378 --> 20:13.463
She always has. She knows.

20:13.964 --> 20:15.549
All right, everybody. It's time.

20:15.632 --> 20:18.552
I'm sorry. I have to go in. I'm sorry.

20:42.910 --> 20:45.954
Those are the winners right there.

20:47.581 --> 20:53.003
And these are the losers.
Can't even pull off a local election.

20:54.755 --> 20:56.840
This is what you've tied yourself to.

20:57.841 --> 20:59.092
Old ideas.

20:59.968 --> 21:02.262
Unpopular. Unwanted.

21:03.388 --> 21:04.389
Tired.

21:06.975 --> 21:09.853
Big fat losers.

21:11.939 --> 21:15.442
That's you, right here, right now.

21:15.984 --> 21:18.195
