21:55.190 --> 21:56.441
Mm-hmm.

21:56.525 --> 21:58.777
-And, yeah, looks good. Yeah.
-It looks good.

21:58.861 --> 22:02.990
Happy to go over it with you
some other time.

22:03.073 --> 22:05.701
