in my opinion, yeah. Okay.

22:06.827 --> 22:07.828
That's fine.

22:08.579 --> 22:09.788
I'm so sorry.

22:09.872 --> 22:12.666
The tension just got us so,
like, you know.

22:13.375 --> 22:15.169
